  <span id="freeText4007495960152377124" style="display:none">Wow...you know the magic you felt the first time you read Harry Potter? Yeah, that.<br />I felt that as I read this book - it's hefty and complex and there are multiple storylines - <br />but, it is SO worth the investment of your time and energy! <br /><br />The genre here is blurry - fantasy, fairy tale, historical fiction, multicultural - what exactly is happening? There is this magical element that is all about the POWER OF MUSIC and that sustained my interest. This book is beautifully written; I laughed, I cried, and the entire fourth part gave me goosebumps as I realized how the threads all came together...<br /><br />This book comes out in February 2015 - do yourself a favor and pre-order it with your local bookseller now!</span>
